pcdp-lint (0.3.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of pcdp-lint
  * Implements Post-Coding Development Paradigm specification validation
  * Supports structural validation of specification files
  * Validates metadata fields including SPDX license identifiers
  * Checks deployment template compliance
  * Provides list-templates command for template discovery

